Linux initrd utilities

Should generate a slackbuild looking like this:
```
./
install/
install/doinst.sh
install/slack-desc
opt/
opt/afterpkg-python/
opt/afterpkg-python/initrd-0.1.tar.gz
usr/
usr/doc/
usr/doc/initrd-0.1/
usr/doc/initrd-0.1/README
usr/doc/initrd-0.1/initrd.SlackBuild
var/
var/lib/
var/lib/pkgtools/
var/lib/pkgtools/douninst.sh/
var/lib/pkgtools/douninst.sh/initrd-0.1-x86_64-1_SBo
```
